    <entry>
      <title>爱快创建OpenWrt虚拟机，自动优选ip</title>
      <link href="/posts/7f46148a.html"/>
      <url>/posts/7f46148a.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="openwrt固件定制地址https-openwrt-ai"><a href="#openwrt固件定制地址https-openwrt-ai" class="headerlink" title="openwrt固件定制地址https://openwrt.ai/"></a>openwrt固件定制地址<a href="https://openwrt.ai/">https://openwrt.ai/</a></h1><h2 id="爱快虚拟机要下载这个固件"><a href="#爱快虚拟机要下载这个固件" class="headerlink" title="爱快虚拟机要下载这个固件"></a>爱快虚拟机要下载这个固件</h2><p><img src="https://image.boring1998.top/file/483a1c9a272b278e88877.png" alt="483a1c9a272b278e88877.png"></p><h2 id="下面是虚拟机设置"><a href="#下面是虚拟机设置" class="headerlink" title="下面是虚拟机设置"></a>下面是虚拟机设置</h2><p><img src="https://image.boring1998.top/file/d92902f35a868f471a011.png" alt="d92902f35a868f471a011.png"></p><h2 id="接下来点击vnc，修改OpenWrt的网络ip"><a href="#接下来点击vnc，修改OpenWrt的网络ip" class="headerlink" title="接下来点击vnc，修改OpenWrt的网络ip"></a>接下来点击vnc，修改OpenWrt的网络ip</h2><p>1、以root的身份登录；<br>2、修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;config&#x2F;network文件：<br>vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;config&#x2F;network<br>按i或者insert键，把 option gateway ‘192.168.1.1’改成自己需要的IP地址，如192.168.100.2，再按ESC键，再按：wq保存退出，重启即可。</p><p>进入OpenWrt的终端，下载优选ip一键脚本<br>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/yonggekkk/openwrt_win64-ddns-cdnip">https://github.com/yonggekkk/openwrt_win64-ddns-cdnip</a></p><p>curl -ksSL <a href="https://gitlab.com/rwkgyg/cdnopw/raw/main/cdnopw.sh">https://gitlab.com/rwkgyg/cdnopw/raw/main/cdnopw.sh</a> -o cdnopw.sh &amp;&amp; bash cdnopw.sh</p><h2 id="设置计划任务定时任务"><a href="#设置计划任务定时任务" class="headerlink" title="设置计划任务定时任务"></a>设置计划任务定时任务</h2><p>每三个小时执行一次</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">30 0 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 3 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 6 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 9 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 12 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 15 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 18 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br><span class="line">30 21 * * * cd /root/cfipopw/ &amp;&amp; bash cdnip.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
